                  </hi>. I am a plumber, and live at Stratford. On the 12th of Feb. I went to the Harrow public-house—I pulled off my coat, which had a handkerchief and a pair of gloves in it—when I went for it it was gone—this is my handkerchief.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> See if there is a hole in the middle of the handkerchief? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes—I swear to it from a small hole in it.</p>
